shapes:EventOfferTemplateShape
    a sh:NodeShape ;
    sh:targetClass ids:EventOffer ;
    sh:node shapes:HasProviderOrConsumerNodeShape ;
    sh:property shapes:EventOfferTemplate-permissionPropertyShape ;
    sh:message "<https://raw.githubusercontent.com/International-Data-Spaces-Association/InformationModel/master/examples/contract-and-usage-policy/templates/EventRestrictedUsage/EventOfferTemplateShape.ttl> (EventOfferTemplateShape): In a _:EventOffer a) the ids:provider property must point to one participant or b) the ids:consumer property must point to one participant or c) the ids:provider and the ids:consumer must point to one participant. This can in any case be a) an IRI or b) an ids:Participant. The ids:permission property must point to exactly one ids:Permission. In the ids:Permission the ids:target and ids:action properties and at least one of (ids:assigner or ids:assignee) pointing to a participant have to be specified. The ids:constraint property must point to an ids:Constraint. Within the constraint the ids:leftOperand specifies an EventURI via rdf:subject and defines ids:broader pointing to idsc:EVENT. The ids:operator must be idsc:EQUALS, the ids:rightOperand must be true as xsd:boolean and the ids:pipEndpoint must specify an EventPipUri."@en ;
.


shapes:EventOfferTemplate-permissionPropertyShape
    a sh:PropertyShape ;
    sh:path ids:permission ;
    sh:class ids:Permission ;
    sh:node shapes:EventOfferPermissionTemplate ;
    sh:minCount 1 ;
    sh:maxCount 1 ;
    sh:severity sh:Violation ;
    sh:message "<https://raw.githubusercontent.com/International-Data-Spaces-Association/InformationModel/master/examples/contract-and-usage-policy/templates/EventRestrictedUsage/EventOfferTemplateShape.ttl> (EventOfferTemplate-permissionPropertyShape): In a _:EventOffer the ids:permission property must point to exactly one ids:Permission. In the ids:Permission the ids:target and ids:action properties and and at least one of (ids:assigner or ids:assignee) pointing to a participant have to be specified. The ids:constraint property must point to an ids:Constraint. Within the constraint the ids:leftOperand specifies an EventURI via rdf:subject and defines ids:broader pointing to idsc:EVENT. The ids:operator must be idsc:EQUALS, the ids:rightOperand must be true as xsd:boolean and the ids:pipEndpoint must specify an EventPipUri."@en ;
.


shapes:EventOfferPermissionTemplate
    a sh:NodeShape ;
    sh:node shapes:HasAssignerOrAssigneeNodeShape ;
    sh:property shapes:PermissionTemplate-targetPropertyShape ;
    sh:property shapes:PermissionTemplate-actionPropertyShape ;
    sh:property shapes:EventPermissionTemplate-constraintPropertyShape ;
.
